&para.seealso.gen;

Examples



Ordinary paragraphs can contain most block elements:



&para.example.1.txt;



&para.example.1.gen;




Formal paragraphs include a title:



&para.example.2.txt;



&para.example.2.gen;




Simple paragraphs may not contain block elements:



&para.example.3.txt;



&para.example.3.gen;


&para.example.seealso.gen;
